20/09/2009
ATHENS, Greece -- Foreign Minister Dora Bakoyannis has been hospitalised with symptoms of pneumonia, her doctors announced Friday (September 18th). The illness was not caused by swine flu, the doctors added. Bakoyannis, 55, announced earlier on her personal website that her agenda is being cleared for the next several days until she recovers. (Kathimerini - 19/09/09; ANA-MPA, AP, ITAR-TASS - 18/09/09)
